[Main]
Title=Bitwise complement operator ('~')
Index=~

[Top]
In the expression
<PRE>~ <I>expr</I>
</PRE>
the <I>expr</I> operand must be of integral type. The result is the bitwise
complement of the operand after any required integral promotions.
Each 0 bit in the operand is set to 1, and each 1 bit in the operand is set to 0.
